  gimp-freetype-0.6.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

  16 Jun 2005; Leonardo Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org>
  gimp-freetype-0.6.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

  05 Jun 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  gimp-freetype-0.5.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

  31 May 2005; Marcus D. Hanwell <cryos@gentoo.org>
  gimp-freetype-0.5.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64.

*gimp-freetype-0.6 (12 May 2005)

  12 May 2005; Leonardo Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org>
  gimp-freetype-0.6.ebuild:
  New release. Style changes.

  02 Aug 2004; L. Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org> gimp-freetype-0.5.ebuild:
  Updated intltool dependency to be >=0.29. See bug #58786.

  07 Jul 2004; Danny van Dyk <kugelfang@gentoo.org> gimp-freetype-0.5.ebuild:
  Marked ~amd64.

  22 Jun 2004; Leonardo Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org>
  gimp-freetype-0.5.ebuild:
  Marked stable on x86.

  25 Apr 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> gimp-freetype-0.2-r3.ebuild:
  Add die following econf for bug 48950

  19 Apr 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> gimp-freetype-0.5.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

*gimp-freetype-0.5 (18 Apr 2004)

  18 Apr 2004; Leonardo Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org>
  gimp-freetype-0.2-r3.ebuild, gimp-freetype-0.5.ebuild:
  New release, works with The Gimp 2.0. Use mirror:// syntax, fixed
  dependencies and SLOT values. Minor cosmetic corrections.

*gimp-freetype-0.2-r3 (16 Jan 2003)

  19 Aug 2003; foser <foser@gentoo.org> gimp-freetype-0.2-r3.ebuild :
  Fix gimp dep (#22843) and fixed dep vars

  16 Jan 2003; Leonardo Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org> : Fix for sandbox
  violation (bug #14030).

  16 Jan 2003; Jared Hudson <jhhudso@gentoo.org> : Fixed install bug where
  gimp-freetype was installing help files to /var/tmp/portage/
	
*gimp-freetype-0.2-r2 (12 Mar 2002)

  12 Mar 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>:
  Added USE dependent nls compilation

*gimp-freetype-0.2-r1 (22 Feb 2002)

  22 Feb 2002; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@gentoo.org>: Added a dep on
  >=media-gfx/gimp-1.2.3-r1 so that gimptool can be found (symlink was missing
  in earlier versions)

*gimp-freetype-0.2 (1 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  
  Added initial ChangeLog which should be updated whenever the package is
  updated in any way. This changelog is targetted to users. This means that the
  comments should well explained and written in clean English. The details about
  writing correct changelogs are explained in the skel.ChangeLog file which you
  can find in the root directory of the portage repository.
